6.1 Dev Environment
- node.js
  - node -v
  - npm -v
- git
- vuejs.org
  - cli 
  - install
  - vue init webpack folder
- webpack

6.2 Structure
- README.md
- package.json
  - depandicies
- package-lock.json
  - dependencies version
- LICENSE
- index.html
  - core
  - main page
- postcssrc.js
  - css
- gitignore
- eslintrc.js
  - code analysis
- eslintignore
  - ignore with eslint
- editorconfig
  - editor 
- babelrc
  - vue single page
  - compile
- /static**
  - static resources
  - pic/mock data
- /src**
  - source
  - main.js
  - app.vue
  - /router
    - index.js
  - /component
    - *.vue
  - /assets
    - *.pic
- /node_modules
  - 3rd party node package
- /config**
  - config file for Environment
- /build
  - webpack config

6.3 Single Component/router
- main.js app -> index.html
  - component: {App : App} -> same key/value -> ES6
- App.vue
  - single component file
  - <template></template>
  - <script></script>   -> method
  - <style></style>
- router  
  - router/index.js
  - app.template -> <router-view>
  - will map the router config to the view/component
  - path mapping localhost:8080/#/path
- Linkage
  - index.html -> app.vue -> router.js -> helloworld.vue